               <msContents>
                  <summary>Law of the Kings, Text and Commentary, <foreign xml:lang="am">መጽሐፈ፡ ፍትሐ፡ ነገሥት፡ ከነትርጓሜው፡, </foreign> Part I,  belonging to Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros Gäbrä Maryam</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="121v" facs="003">Fols 1r–121v</locus>
                    <title>Code of the Kings, Text and Commentary, Mäṣǝḥafä Fǝtǝḥa Nägäśt Känätǝrgwamew, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ፡ ፍትሐ፡ ነገሥት፡ ከነትርጓሜው፡</foreign>, Part I</title>
                    <note>For part II see EMIP 689</note>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="25v" facs="003">Fols 1r–25v</locus>
                    <title>Introduction and Table of Contents</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወስነ፡ ሠርሖቱ፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መቅድመ፡ ጉባኤ፡ ዘአስተጋብእዎ፡ ሊቃውንት፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡ ወበረከቶሙ፡ የሃሉ። </foreign>
                        <foreign xml:lang="am">ይህን መጽሐፍ፡ ጌታ፡ ሰው፡ በሆነ፡ በ፫፻፴፭ ዘየዓቢ፡ ቈስጠንጢኖስ፡ በነገሠ፡ በ፲፱ ዘመን፡ በኒቅያ፡ ጉባኤ፡ የተሰብሰቡ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                      </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                    <locus from="26r" to="121v" facs="028">Fols 26r–121v</locus>
                    <title>Commentary on Ecclesiastical laws</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዋህድ፡ በመለኮት፡ ዘይሤለስ፡ በአካላት፡ ወኵናታት። </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="am">በመግዛት፡ በመፍጠር፡ አንድ፡ በአካል፡ ሦስት፡ በሚሆን፡ በእግዚአብሔር፡ ስም፡ አምነን፡
                        ክፍል፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ የምንጽፈው፡ መጀመሪያው፡ አንቀጽ፡ ይህ፡ ነው። </foreign>
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡<gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </incipit>
                </msItem>
              </msItem>
